<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得赶到美罗城会展中心。”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要找出谁偷了珠宝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了看朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我马上就回来。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我刚想起来，我忘了遛狗了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。”特勒尔说，“一会儿......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跑远了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西到了美罗城会展中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到一群人站在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看起来很难过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的珠宝展示柜都是空的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”史密斯侦探看到罗西后叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你来了，我很高兴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“您在这里干什么，侦探先生？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>要买钻石戒指吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！”史密斯侦探假装笑道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这次很严重，火箭女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人偷了很多名贵的珠宝。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您找到什么线索了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，这不是今晚唯一的抢劫案。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城大酒店舞会上的珠宝也被偷了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”罗西说，“也许是同一个小偷干的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两次偷的都是珠宝。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”一个男人说，“非常名贵的珠宝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些可怕的小偷，偷走了我所有珍贵的绿宝石。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们偷走了我的红宝石耳环！”一个高个子女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有我的钻石太阳镜！”一个老太太说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她吸了吸鼻子。“那是我最喜欢的太阳镜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人能告诉我刚才发生了什么事吗？”史密斯侦探问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从口袋拿出一个小本子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人看到什么了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>高个子女人走上前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我什么都没看见。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，我听到了声音，很大的轰鸣声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>听起来像是几辆摩托车的声音。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也听到了轰鸣声。”男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，是嗞嗞的声音。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一道闪电出现了。”他的妻子补充说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接着，灯光都熄灭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当灯光再亮时，所有的珠宝都不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些小偷还偷走了我的新钻石头冠。”另一个女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我本来想戴它参加明天的展会。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么展会？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不知道吗？”老太太惊讶地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王冠珠宝将在美罗城博物馆展出。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王冠珠宝非常华丽。”男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们今天才到美罗城，明天将对外展示。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是世界上最大，最名贵的珠宝。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西倒吸一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道小偷接下来要偷什么了——王冠珠宝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>